> 
>> +	sdata->reset_gpio = devm_gpiod_get_optional(dev, "reset",
>> +						    GPIOD_OUT_HIGH);
> 
> Are you really sure the reset is active-high?

This is not choice of ACTIVE HIGH here. It's initialization to logical
level to keep device in reset state.

